			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">MT group bard role in raid<a name="32912"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 5 04 10:18 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>We are having a spirited discussion in out guild regarding what songs should be sung on the MT during a raid by the bard in the MT's group. Without biasing the topic with our discussion, I would love the forum members to give their view as to the best three songs to twist to support an MT during a raid. If you use a different combination for different mobs, please tell us the combo's you use for that mob. For, example: against MM, as a bard with no SM AA or other singing mods, I twist Elemental Chorus, Guardian Ryhthms and CHA buff. The MT reports that he resists all of MM's procs when I do this.
<br />

<br />
What are your twists to support your MT?</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%"><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=679798>Brexan</a></span></td>
