				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: MT group bard role in raid<a name="33447"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 7 04 5:12 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>The higher the CHA of a character on whom <span class="Highlight"><a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=1546">Divine Intervention</a> </span> has been cast, the higher the odds that the DI will completely heal them. Therefore the bard indirectly helps keep the MT at full health.</span></td>
